DOS 3.3 DSK Filesystem
-----------------------

## TODO

[ ] Definitely need to implement my own FileSystem, but I should use file.go's
    memFS for inspiration, especially creating a new memFile per OpenFile req.

[ ] Would be cool to generate index.html on the fly. Not listed, but if asked for. (Or redirected?)
