```
$ go run examples/dos33 DISK.DSK
Serving DOS 3.3 DSK filesystem over WebDAV
  Address: http://127.0.0.1:33333/dos33

$ ls -l /Volumes/dos33  # WebDAV mounted here
README
DISK.DSK/

$ head -3 /Volumes/dos33/README
DOS 3.3 DSK Filesystem Folder Structure

Each DSK is represented as a folder with the following files and folders.

$ cd /Volumes/dos33/DISK.DSK
$ ls -1
files/
CATALOG
applesoft/
binary/
intbasic/
text/
a/
b/
r/
s/
locks/   # Might be unnecessary
VTOC

$ cat CATALOG

DISK VOLUME 254

 I 002 HELLO
*I 043 APPLESOFT
 I 016 ANIMALS
 I 009 COLOR DEMOS
*I 004 MASTER.CREATE
*B 039 RAWDOS
*I 007 COPY
*B 007 COPY.OBJ


$ ls -1 files/
HELLO
APPLESOFT
ANIMALS
COLOR DEMOS
MASTER.CREATE
RAWDOS
COPY
COPY.OBJ

$ ls -1 applesoft/

$ ls -1 intbasic/
HELLO
APPLESOFT
ANIMALS
COLOR DEMOS
MASTER.CREATE
COPY

$ hexdump -C files/HELLO | head -2  # files/ contains raw binary
00000000  01 a5 27 c9 09 d0 18 a5  2b 4a 4a 4a 4a 09 c0 85  |..'.....+JJJJ...|
00000010  3f a9 5c 85 3e 18 ad fe  08 6d ff 08 8d fe 08 ae  |?.\.>....m......|

$ cat intbasic/HELLO
10  PRINT "HI"
20  GOTO 10

$ ls -1 locks/
APPLESOFT
MASTER.CREATE
RAWDOS
COPY
COPY.OBJ

$ touch locks/HELLO
$ ls -1 locks/
HELLO
APPLESOFT
MASTER.CREATE
RAWDOS
COPY
COPY.OBJ

$ cat CATALOG

DISK VOLUME 254

*I 002 HELLO
*I 043 APPLESOFT
 I 016 ANIMALS
 I 009 COLOR DEMOS
*I 004 MASTER.CREATE
*B 039 RAWDOS
*I 007 COPY
*B 007 COPY.OBJ

```